    dc:description "FIGURES 1A–D. Dendrolycosa sahyadriensis spec. nov. A. Male, dorsal view; B. Same, ventral view; C. Female, dorsal view; D. Same ventral view. Scale bars: A–B: 2mm. C–D: 5 mm." ;
